transArray.content: It's pretty good. There's only one inner cabin left. It's very clean. The bed is very comfortable and the bath water is good. There are many bottles of mineral water in the room and there's a small refrigerator! Very good ~ mainly because I like robot food delivery
A word of affirmation and a slight smile are all great affirmations of Xiao Ji's work. Xiao Ji pursues to do better.
